'''''Viridium''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttle]] of the same group as [[Tydirium/Legends|''Tydirium'']]. It was stationed at [[Outpost 327]], when the latter was captured by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] during their [[Mission to Zhar|preparations]] for the upcoming [[Battle of Endor/Legends|attack]] on the [[Death Star II/Legends|Death Star II]] at [[Endor/Legends|Endor]].

